Package: ids2names
Title: ID to name converter
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Christopher Bottoms [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Christopher Bottoms <molecules@cpan.org>
Description: Given a vector of reference IDs, a vector of their corresponding matching names, and a vector of input IDs, return their matching names if they exist or simply the original ID for cases in which the IDs were not in the reference.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
